WEBVTT

00:03:58.600 --> 00:04:00.896
And I know you're
wondering about this one.

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:03.336
Yes, they kiss too,

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:05.056
sometimes very deeply.

00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:08.296
(Applause)

00:04:08.320 --> 00:04:10.896
Some have even learned
to cheat on their spouses.

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:11.936
(Laughter)

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.936
For example, the African jacana:

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:16.375
the females will mate with multiple males

00:04:16.399 --> 00:04:19.336
and then she takes off
to find other males to mate with

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:22.536
and she leaves the male behind
to take care of the chicks.

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.176
(Laughter)

00:04:24.200 --> 00:04:27.360
(Applause)

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:30.336
And birds help us so much,